{"tid":1762850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(公投)有幾多人一世都唔會原諒黑警？","createTime":"2019-11-30T01:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T01:47:24.000Z","uid":152701,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0fe3d06150dfb844c434cf100755df9bc64f7eda","tid":1762850,"uid":152701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:36:47.000Z","msg":"黑警！還眼！<br />\n黑警！填命！<br />\n好嬲好嬲！<br />\n應承我！一世都唔會原諒黑警！<br />\n投票表達意向！我地香港人一定贏！<br />\n正皮：原諒<br />\n負皮：唔原諒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩！好多票！大勝！贏！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">跟住呢？</span></span><br />\n重建連儂牆慢過閪<br />\n文宣滲透率低到見都見唔到咁濟<br />\n參與集會遊行嘅人少過以前八成<br />\n成班六月打飛機打到而家<br />\n講到自己真係贏撚左咁<br />\n黑警連毛都冇還過一條<br />\n成班仲係度打飛機區選區選立法會<br />\n<br />\n由打破制度 變返 回歸制度<br />\n由時代革命 變返 研究點樣係<strong>已有</strong>制度到贏<br />\n<br />\n已有制度入面贏到 你地六月就街都唔洗上啦<br />\n簡單一句<br />\n邊個仲研究咩「立法會」點贏嘅人<br />\n放心 你地唔係鬼<br />\n但你地智商低到令到你地嘅所作所為比鬼更衰<br />\n<br />\n醒少少 做返啲實事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e8c1bb12d070182f47f6f786c89154aedb1b8a","tid":1762850,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72k1rM4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72k1rM4.png&h=eddfba7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/javwOZm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjavwOZm.jpg&h=077ca37a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hE9ADA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hE9ADA.jpg&h=be8cfb76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>運動未完 仍需努力</strong></span><br />\n12月8 民陣轉咗遊行"}]}